                        <div class="row">

                            <div class="form-group col-md-4">
                                <label for="">Sum Total Sanctioned Rs. <span id="val">.</span></label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group col-md-2"></div>
                            <div class="form-group col-md-4">
                                <label for="">Application Sanction. <span id="appsanc">.</span></label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p>The Medical Bills Which are sanctioned.are found in order if approved we may pay Rs.<span id="value">.</span></p>
                        <p>to the employees for the above sanctioned cases as mentioned in annexure(enclosed).</p>
                        <p>Submitted for Approval Please.</p>
                        <p>A.M(SK)</p>
                        <p>SVP(SS)</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
